  "id": 784,
  "type": "Statement",
  "description": "The European Medicines Agency (EMA) has authorized pembrolizumab in combination with trastuzumab, fluoropyrimidine and platinum-containing chemotherapy for the first-line treatment of adult patients with locally advanced unresectable or metastatic HER2-positive gastric or gastro-esophageal junction adenocarcinoma whose tumors express PD-L1 with a combined positive score (CPS) >= 1.",
